.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He can also become the first artistic gymnast to win four medals in one event.\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A Division ofNBCUniversal.\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1272, \"end\": 1282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9999978029263992, \"rank\": 2.197038601830534e-06, \"text\": \"A Division\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DISCLAIMER: This site and the products offered are for entertainment purposes only, and there is no gambling offered on this site.\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1430, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This service is intended for adult audiences.\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1476, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No guarantees are made for any specific outcome.\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1525, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, please call 1-800-GAMBLER.\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1603, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u24b8 2024 NBC Universal\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": []}]}"